title: Bow of a ship

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a bow of a ship, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a front and bottom perspective view of a bow of a ship, showing my new design;
FIG. 2 is a front, side and bottom perspective view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a side elevational view thereof;
FIG. 4 is a bottom, front and side perspective view thereof; and,
FIG. 5 is a side elevational view thereof from the side opposite that shown in FIG. 3.
The interior of the bow is not seen in use and its appearance is not claimed.
